# 🥗 Healthy Herbivore Kiosk

A modern self-service restaurant kiosk application designed for the Healthy Herbivore concept.
The kiosk allows customers to quickly browse the menu, customize their order, and place it without staff assistance.

The system focuses on speed, clarity, and dietary transparency, ensuring customers can easily identify vegan and vegetarian options before ordering.

# 📌 Overview

The Healthy Herbivore Kiosk is an interactive touchscreen interface placed inside the restaurant. It guides customers through the entire ordering process:

- Choose how they want to dine.
- Select their preferred language.
- Browse the menu.
- View dietary information.
- Add items to their cart.
- Edit or remove items.
- Place the order and receive a receipt.
- The goal is to reduce queue times, improve customer experience, and clearly communicate plant-based dietary options.

# ✨ Features
🖥️ Kiosk Welcome Screen

Customers begin by selecting how they want to enjoy their order:

- To-Go
- Eat Here

# 🌍 Language Selection

The kiosk supports multiple languages so customers can interact with the system comfortably.
Example languages:

- English
- Dutch

# 📋 Menu Browsing

Customers can easily browse through the restaurant’s menu.
Each menu item includes:

- Name
- Description
- Price
- Dietary label

# 🌱 Dietary Indicators

Transparency is a core goal of the Healthy Herbivore project.
Menu items clearly show whether they are:

- Vegan 🌱
- Vegetarian 🥬

This helps customers make quick and informed choices.

# 🛒 Cart System

Customers can add items to their cart while browsing.
Cart functionality includes:

- Add items
- Remove items
- Change quantity
- Edit selections
- View order total

# ✏️ Order Editing

Before placing the order, customers can review their cart and:

- Modify item quantities
- Remove items
- Review pricing

This ensures order accuracy.

# 🧾 Order Placement & Receipt

Once satisfied with their order, customers can:

- Place the order
- Receive a receipt with order details

The receipt includes:

- Ordered items
- Total price
- Order number
- Dining option (Eat Here / To-Go)